Linux
~/.bashrc         <--script file that's executed when a user logs in
~/.bash_logout    
~/.bash_profile   <-- export path
~/.bash_history   <-- history of user activities

git
.gitignore        <--  A gitignore file specifies intentionally untracked files that Git should ignore, .gitignore file must be edited and committed by hand when you have new files that you wish to ignore.
